            </ul>
            <a href="tel:9038405725" class="btn" style="padding: 10px 20px; font-size: 1rem;">Call (903) 840-5725</a>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section id="home" class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>Expert Remodeling & Handyman Services in Canton, TX</h1>
            <p>Over 40 years of craftsmanship you can trust. Residential & Commercial. Quality work that lasts.</p>
            <div>
                <a href="#contact" class="btn">Get Your Free Estimate</a>
                <a href="tel:9038405725" class="btn btn-secondary">Call Now</a>
            </div>
            <p style="margin-top: 2rem; font-size: 1.1rem;">Proudly serving Canton and surrounding East Texas communities</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Services -->
    <section id="services">
        <h2>Our Services</h2>
        <div class="services-grid">
            <div class="service-card">
                <img src="https://picsum.photos/id/1015/600/400" alt="Kitchen Remodeling">
                <div class="service-card-content">
                    <h3>Residential Remodeling</h3>
                    <p>Kitchens, bathrooms, room additions, and full home renovations with attention to detail.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="service-card">
                <img src="https://picsum.photos/id/201/600/400" alt="Commercial Remodeling">
                <div class="service-card-content">
                    <h3>Commercial Services</h3>
                    <p>Office build-outs, retail renovations, tenant improvements, and professional commercial projects.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="service-card">
                <img src="https://picsum.photos/id/251/600/400" alt="Handyman">
                <div class="service-card-content">
                    <h3>Handyman Services</h3>
                    <p>Small repairs, installations, maintenance, and everything in between. No job too small.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="service-card">
                <img src="https://picsum.photos/id/301/600/400" alt="Painting">
                <div class="service-card-content">
                    <h3>Painting & Drywall</h3>
                    <p>Interior/exterior painting, drywall repair and installation, texture matching.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="service-card">
                <img src="https://picsum.photos/id/133/600/400" alt="Flooring">
                <div class="service-card-content">
                    <h3>Flooring Installation</h3>
                    <p>Laminate, hardwood, tile, and luxury vinyl plank flooring. Professional results.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- About -->
    <section id="about" class="about">
        <h2>About Cedar Creek Carpentry</h2>
        <div class="about-grid">
            <div>
                <h3>40+ Years of Trusted Craftsmanship</h3>
                <p>Owned and operated by Chris Splawn, Cedar Creek Carpentry brings decades of hands-on experience to every project. From simple repairs to complete transformations, we treat your home or business with the same care we would our own.</p>
                
                <div class="experience-badge">
                    <strong>40+</strong><br>
                    Years Experience
                </div>
                
                <p>We specialize in both residential and commercial remodeling throughout the Canton, Texas area. Our commitment to quality materials, clean work sites, and honest communication has earned us the trust of homeowners and business owners alike.</p>
                
                <ul style="margin-top: 2rem; line-height: 2;">
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check" style="color: var(--accent); margin-right: 10px;"></i> Licensed & Insured</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check" style="color: var(--accent); margin-right: 10px;"></i> Free Estimates</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check" style="color: var(--accent); margin-right: 10px;"></i> On-Time Completion</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check" style="color: var(--accent); margin-right: 10px;"></i> Customer Satisfaction Guaranteed</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
                <img src="https://picsum.photos/id/1016/700/500" alt="Chris Splawn - Owner" style="width:100%; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);">
                <p style="text-align:center; margin-top: 1rem; font-style:italic;">Chris Splawn, Owner & Lead Carpenter</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Testimonials -->
    <section id="testimonials" class="testimonials">
        <h2 style="color:white;">What Our Clients Say</h2>
        <div class="testimonial-grid">
            <div class="testimonial">
                <p>"Chris and his team transformed our outdated kitchen into a modern masterpiece. Professional, clean, and on budget. Highly recommend!"</p>
                <p><strong>— Sarah M., Canton, TX</strong></p>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial">
                <p>"Needed several small repairs around the house. Cedar Creek handled everything quickly and at a fair price. Will definitely use them again."</p>
                <p><strong>— Michael R., Edgewood, TX</strong></p>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial">
                <p>"Commercial tenant improvement project went smoothly from start to finish. Attention to detail was impressive."</p>
                <p><strong>— David L., Business Owner</strong></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Free Estimate Form -->
    <section id="contact">
        <h2>Get Your Free Estimate Today</h2>
        <div class="contact-form">
            <form action="https://formspree.io/f/YOUR_FORM_ID_HERE" method="POST" id="estimate-form">
                <div class="form-grid">
                    <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Your Full Name" required>
                    <input type="tel" name="phone" placeholder="Phone Number" required>
                </div>
                
                <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Email Address">
                
                <select name="service-type" required>
                    <option value="">Select Service Type</option>
                    <option value="residential">Residential Remodeling</option>
                    <option value="commercial">Commercial Remodeling</option>
                    <option value="handyman">Handyman / Small Repairs</option>
                    <option value="painting">Painting & Drywall</option>
                    <option value="flooring">Flooring Installation</option>
                    <option value="other">Other</option>
                </select>
                
                <textarea name="project-details" rows="6" placeholder="Please describe your project or what you need help with..."></textarea>
                
                <input type="text" name="address" placeholder="Project Address (Canton, TX area)">
                
                <button type="submit" class="btn" style="width: 100%; padding: 16px; font-size: 1.1rem;">Submit Request for Free Estimate</button>
            </form>
            <p style="text-align:center; margin-top: 1.5rem; font-size: 0.95rem; color: #666;">
                We typically respond within 24 hours. For urgent needs, please call <strong>(903) 840-5725</strong>.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer>
        <div class="footer-grid">
            <div>
                <h3 style="color:white; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Cedar Creek Carpentry</h3>
                <p>Canton, Texas</p>
                <p>Serving East Texas with pride</p>
                <p style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
                    <a href="tel:9038405725" style="color: var(--accent); font-size: 1.4rem; text-decoration: none;">
                        (903) 840-5725
                    </a>
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div>
                <h4 style="color:white; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Quick Links</h4>
                <ul style="list-style: none; line-height: 2.2;">
                    <li><a href="#services" style="color:#ccc; text-decoration:none;">Services</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#about" style="color:#ccc; text-decoration:none;">About Chris Splawn</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#contact" style="color:#ccc; text-decoration:none;">Free Estimates</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div>
                <h4 style="color:white; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Hours</h4>
                <p>Monday - Friday: 7:00 AM - 6:00 PM<br>
                Saturday: By Appointment<br>
                Sunday: Closed</p>
                
                <p style="margin-top: 2rem;">
                    <strong>Licensed • Insured • Bonded</strong>
                </p>
